### 第一週/第二週：健康檢查與全部醫師
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health
Accept: application/json

###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctors
Accept: application/json

###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctors?department=內科

###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D001

###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D999


### === 以下為本週 (Ch09-C) 新增的 API 測試 === ###

### 新增一位醫師 (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/doctors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctorId": "D006",
  "name": "測試醫師",
  "department": "內科",
  "specialty": "測試專長"
}

### 更新剛剛的醫師 (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D006
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試醫師",
  "department": "內科",
  "specialty": "專長已被修改"
}

### 刪除該醫師 (DELETE)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/D006

### 取得所有病患
GET http://localhost:8080/api/patients

### 取得掛號總數
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments/count

### 依日期篩選掛號
GET http://localhost:8080/api/appointments?date=2026-05-20